<br>
I have heard people state that it's &quot;unkillable,&quot; and am just wondering how true this really is.  Is it possible that those guilds that have tried simply didn't find the right strategy?<br>
<br>
Has anyone heard of an Uber Guild going back to try the sleeper again since they attained 65 and gear etc...  I am aware that our own sleeper is not awake, but was wondering about other servers.  I also admit that I do not know which servers have a Sleeper that's awake.<br>
<br>
