<br>
&quot;Begone insect, I have much slaying to do!&quot;<br>
<br>
Then zones out and proceeds to make his way to Lord Yelinak, killing off everyone in his path, until he reaches Yelinak, kills him, and then despawns.  Forever, along with the 4 warders, which means no more Primal Weaponry for you!  (and most likely a hate list so huge that EQ would become unplayable!)<br>
<br>
Lady Vox shouts, ‘The Sleeper stirs! A glorious new age for Norrath is about to begin, and my exile will soon end!’ <br>
<br>
A guardian of skyshrine shouts, ‘BEWARE! BEWARE! The Sleeper has been awakened! Flee the shrine immediately, he intends death to all here!’ <br>
<br>
The Sleeper shouts, ‘I AM FREE!’ <br>
<br>
Really, it's an exercise in futility to release Kerafrym, and insanely stupid.  However, I believe that for servers such as Xev who had restraint in releasing Kerafrym, will be rewarded in some way with a neat ending.  This story, is not done yet.<br>
